sentence: What prerequisites do I still need to take in order to take EECS 489 ?
sentence-with-vars: What prerequisites do I still need to take in order to take department0 number0 ?
sql: SELECT DISTINCT COURSEalias0.NAME , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE AS COURSEalias1 , COURSE_PREREQUISITE AS COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0.PRE_COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID NOT IN ( SELECT STUDENT_RECORDalias0.COURSE_ID FROM STUDENT_RECORD AS STUDENT_RECORDalias0 WHERE STUDENT_RECORDalias0.STUDENT_ID = 1 ) AND COURSEalias1.COURSE_ID = COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0.COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias1.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias1.NUMBER = 489 ;
